WEBVTT

00:14:29.784 --> 00:14:32.175
there was no wiggle and waggle,

00:14:32.199 --> 00:14:35.028
there was no spend-five-minutes-
to-come-back-to-the-point.

00:14:35.052 --> 00:14:36.720
I didn't have to keep interrupting,

00:14:36.744 --> 00:14:38.827
which I've become rather
renowned for doing,

00:14:38.851 --> 00:14:41.383
because I want people
to answer the question.

00:14:41.407 --> 00:14:43.458
And he answered me,

00:14:43.482 --> 00:14:46.096
and it was pretty interesting.

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:47.551
And he said --

00:14:47.575 --> 00:14:49.353
CH: Tell me what he said.

00:14:49.377 --> 00:14:50.597
CA: No, no, you go ahead.

00:14:50.621 --> 00:14:52.849
CH: You're the interrupter,
I'm the listener.

00:14:52.873 --> 00:14:54.031
CA: No, no, go ahead.

00:14:54.055 --> 00:14:55.210
CH: What'd he say?

00:14:55.234 --> 00:14:58.312
CA: OK. You've talked about
nationalism and tribalism here today.

00:14:58.336 --> 00:15:02.098
I asked him, "How did you have the guts
to confront the prevailing winds